description:
Sharing the product I use to enable Video, Apple Carplay, Android Auto, and YouTube on the top screen of my 2015+ Infiniti Q50 (works with Q60 too).  Stick around - in this video I show how to enable Video in Motion/Video while driving (offroad use only)

I'VE UPGRADED TO THE G-SERIES! It does everything this screen does, and MORE:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mp3OE77U0AY

GET ONE: https://bit.ly/GSeries-Q50

STILL WANT A SMARTAUTOKITS? :
https://squarewheelsauto.com/products/smartautokits-android-tablet-interface-w-apple-carplay-android-auto

Buy me a beer:
https://www.buymeacoffee.com/squarewheels

Chapters
0:00 - Intro
0:32 - OE Top Screen is Useless
0:57 - Only works with 2015+ Q50/Q60
1:15 - SmartAutoKits Interface Overview
1:37 - How to Enable Video while Driving
2:08 - Outro.  Thanks!
